sub_title: Team Leader and Product Owner - Embedded Software
summary:
Team Leader and Product Owner of an Embedded Software department of ASML.
Leading multiple agile software teams in a challenging and dynamic environment.

Formerly enjoyed working in different roles in the Netherlands, Asia and USA.
From developing (embedded) software, 
to managing high-tech lithographic system upgrades at semiconductor factories worldwide.
Resulting in a balanced mix of technical, operational and customer leadership.
Specialised in new product introduction.
